$ R: .Rprofile file
@ .Rprofile

The `.Rprofile` file is an R script that is read (→ development/languages/R/functions/source[source'd]) when R starts up.
-
The file is not read if the `--no-init-file` → development/languages/R/command-line/startup-options[command line option] is specified.

sa:
`→ Linux/fhs/home/username/_Rprofile`

 → development/languages/R/files
